title: PML-N’s Malik Ghulam Habib wins PP-154 election
content:
ISLAMABAD, Feb 9 (APP): Pakistan Muslim League Nawaz (PML-N) candidate, Malik Ghulam Habib has won the election for Punjab Assembly constituency PP-154, Lahore-X by securing 26,014 votes.
According to the unofficial result issued by the Returning Officer/ECP, his runner-up was independent candidate, Shakeel Ahmad who bagged 24,156 votes.
Overall voters’ turn-out remained 48.23%.
